# Restaurant Reservation & Review Platform - Implementation Plan

A full-stack MERN application for restaurant reservations, reviews, real-time availability, and management dashboards. Built with React + Vite + TailwindCSS frontend and Express + MongoDB backend.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is a very large project. I propose building it in **incremental phases**, starting with Phase 1 (Foundation + Backend + Auth + Public Pages) as a single initial batch. Each phase will be verified before moving to the next. **Do you want me to proceed with Phase 1 first, or would you prefer a different ordering?**

> [!NOTE]
> **Payment**: Using **Razorpay** (test mode). Will ask for API keys when implementing Phase 2.
>
> **Database**: MongoDB Atlas URI provided — will be stored in `server/.env`.
>
> TailwindCSS v4 `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin is already configured (no config file needed).

