#### [NEW] Frontend folder structure:
```
src/
├── components/
│   ├── common/          (Navbar, Footer, LoadingSpinner, StarRating)
│   ├── home/            (Hero, SearchBar, FeaturedRestaurants, etc.)
│   ├── restaurant/      (RestaurantCard, MenuCard, ReviewCard, etc.)
