### 1B. Backend Foundation

#### [NEW] Backend folder structure:
```
server/
├── controllers/   (authController, restaurantController, reservationController, etc.)
├── models/        (User, Restaurant, Reservation, Review, SupportTicket)
├── services/      (razorpay.js)
├── routes/        (authRoutes, restaurantRoutes, reservationRoutes, etc.)
├── middleware/     (auth.js, roleAuth.js, errorHandler.js, upload.js)
├── config/        (db.js)
├── utils/         (generateToken.js, seedData.js)
├── server.js
├── package.json
└── .env           (MONGO_URI, JWT_SECRET, RAZORPAY keys)
```

#### Database Models (Mongoose)

**User**: name, email, password (hashed), role (`customer`|`owner`|`admin`), phone, avatar, favorites[], createdAt

**Restaurant**: name, owner (ref User), description, cuisine[], location (address, city, state, coordinates), priceRange (1-4), images[], phone, email, website, hours (openTime, closeTime, days), totalTables, reservedTables, tableTypes [{type, capacity, count}], menu [{name, description, price, category, image, dietary[]}], features (outdoorSeating, liveMusic, wifi, parking, privateEvents), ambiance, rating (avg), totalReviews, isActive, crowdStatus

**Reservation**: user (ref), restaurant (ref), date, time, guests, tableType, meals [{menuItemId, quantity, price}], eventType (none|birthday|corporate|anniversary), eventDetails {decoration, specialRequest}, totalAmount, paymentStatus, paymentId, status (pending|confirmed|cancelled|completed), notes, createdAt

**Review**: user (ref), restaurant (ref), rating (1-5), comment, images[], ownerReply {text, date}, isEdited, createdAt

**SupportTicket**: user (ref), restaurant (ref), category, subject, description, status (open|in-progress|resolved|closed), ownerReply, adminReply, createdAt

#### API Endpoints

| Method | Route | Description |
|--------|-------|-------------|
| POST | `/api/auth/register` | Register user |
| POST | `/api/auth/login` | Login |
| GET | `/api/auth/me` | Get current user |
| GET | `/api/restaurants` | List/search restaurants |
| GET | `/api/restaurants/:id` | Get restaurant details |
| POST | `/api/restaurants` | Create restaurant (owner) |
| PUT | `/api/restaurants/:id` | Update restaurant (owner) |
| DELETE | `/api/restaurants/:id` | Delete restaurant (admin) |
| POST | `/api/reservations` | Book reservation |
| GET | `/api/reservations/my` | User's reservations |
| PUT | `/api/reservations/:id` | Modify reservation |
| DELETE | `/api/reservations/:id` | Cancel reservation |
| POST | `/api/reviews` | Add review |
| GET | `/api/reviews/restaurant/:id` | Get restaurant reviews |
| PUT | `/api/reviews/:id` | Edit review |
| DELETE | `/api/reviews/:id` | Delete review |
| PUT | `/api/reviews/:id/reply` | Owner reply |
| POST | `/api/payments/create` | Create payment |
| POST | `/api/payments/verify` | Verify payment |
| POST | `/api/support` | Create ticket |
| GET | `/api/support/my` | User's tickets |
| PUT | `/api/support/:id/reply` | Reply to ticket |
| GET | `/api/admin/users` | List users (admin) |
| GET | `/api/admin/stats` | Dashboard stats (admin) |

