### 1C. Public Pages (Phase 1 UI)

**Home Page** - Premium landing page with:
- Navbar with auth buttons and user dropdown
- Hero with large background image + floating search bar
- Featured restaurants grid (3-4 cards)
- "How it works" section (3 steps)
- Events showcase section
- Live crowd status preview
- Testimonials carousel
- CTA section
- Footer

**Restaurant Listing** - Search results with:
- Filter sidebar (cuisine, price, rating, features)
- Restaurant cards grid with images, ratings, price
- Sort options (rating, price, name)
- Pagination

**Restaurant Details** - Full restaurant profile with:
- Image gallery
- Info section (hours, cuisine, price, location)
- Menu section with category tabs
- Reviews section with ratings breakdown
- Sticky reservation panel (right side)
- Crowd status indicator

**Login/Signup Pages** - Clean auth forms with validation

