## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- **Frontend build**: `cd Frontend && npm run build` — must compile without errors
- **Backend start**: `cd server && node server.js` — must start without errors
- **API testing**: Use browser subagent to test API endpoints via the running server

### Browser-Based Verification
- Navigate to `http://localhost:5173` and verify:
  - Home page renders correctly with all sections
  - Navbar, hero, search bar, featured restaurants, footer
  - Restaurant listing page with filter sidebar
  - Restaurant details page layout
  - Login/Signup forms
  - Responsive design on different screen sizes

### Manual Verification
- User should check visual design matches the OpenTable/Airbnb premium aesthetic
- User should test booking flow end-to-end
- User should test payment in Stripe test mode
